item.title: CVE-2022-1906|2024-08-03T00:17:00.966Z -- unknown -- copyright%20proof
item.description: The Copyright Proof WordPress plugin through 4.16 does not sanitise and escape a parameter before outputting it back via an AJAX action available to both unauthenticated and authenticated users, leading to a Reflected Cross-Site Scripting when a specific setting is enabled.
